CREATE TABLE `service_snapshot_script` (
	`id` BIGINT(20) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
	`create_time` TIMESTAMP NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
	`update_time` TIMESTAMP NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
	`create_user` BIGINT(20) NULL DEFAULT NULL,
	`update_user` BIGINT(20) NULL DEFAULT NULL,
	`is_delete` TINYINT(1) NULL DEFAULT '0',
	`version` INT(11) NULL DEFAULT '0',
	`snapshot_no` VARCHAR(50) NULL DEFAULT NULL COMMENT '快照唯一编号' COLLATE 'utf8mb4_general_ci',
	`service_name` VARCHAR(255) NULL DEFAULT NULL COMMENT '服务名称' COLLATE 'utf8mb4_general_ci',
	`service_version` VARCHAR(255) NULL DEFAULT NULL COMMENT 'release版本' COLLATE 'utf8mb4_general_ci',
	`script_type` TINYINT(4) NULL DEFAULT NULL COMMENT '脚本类型1 ddl 2 dml',
	`script` TEXT NULL DEFAULT NULL COMMENT '脚本' COLLATE 'utf8mb4_general_ci',
	PRIMARY KEY (`id`) USING BTREE
)
COMMENT='服务快照脚本'
COLLATE='utf8mb4_general_ci'
ENGINE=InnoDB
AUTO_INCREMENT=2
;
